{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──3个月后。\n整体院已经成为预约都排不上的超人气店铺。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "老师，早上好...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈，今天又是一大早来。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "是的...想尽快接受治疗...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "听你这么说我很高兴"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "而且...最近身体一直很奇怪...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "嗯？怎么了？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "明明还什么都没做...乳头就...疼得不行...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "胸罩一摩擦...就会发出声音...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(即使隔着衬衫，也能清楚地看到凸起...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "下面也是...走路时的摩擦...大腿都湿透了...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(还没换衣服就已经准备好了...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "昨天治疗的余韵还在...想快点进行下一次...拜托了...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "真拿你没办法。今天也会好好给你做的。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(完美...已经是离不开我的身体了...)"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "那个...今天也要'特别疗程'...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "啊，特别性感按摩疗程呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "性、性感!?",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "啊，说错了。是特别整体按摩疗程。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "(...但也许没说错...)",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "还是做普通疗程吧？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "不、不要...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_011"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "普通疗程...已经不能满足了...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_012"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "所以...'特别疗程'...拜托了。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_013"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "如果想接受特别疗程..."
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "我需要确认奈奈是真的想要，得让我好好看看。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_surprised_sweat",
      "text": "咦...？",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_014"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "你知道该怎么做吧？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "那、那是...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_015"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "如果真的想接受特别疗程，就要自己做好准备。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_closeeyes_closemouth",
      "text": "...我明白了...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_016"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈用颤抖的手慢慢开始脱衣服。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "outfit": "naked",
      "text": "老、老师...请看...",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_017"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "全裸的奈奈害羞地用双手掰开了私处。",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "这、这里...已经...这么湿了...",
      "fullImage": "end_true",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_018"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "特别疗程...拜托了...请在这里...做吧...♡",
      "fullImage": "end_true",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_019"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "爱液顺着大腿流下，开始在地板上形成小水洼。",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "很好...学会了自己展示并请求。",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "因为...已经忍不住了...",
      "fullImage": "end_true",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_020"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "真厉害...我还没碰呢...阴蒂都勃起了...湿透了...",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "乳头也肿得这么厉害...",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "原本淡粉色的乳头经过反复的治疗变得敏感，现在充血肿胀成红色。",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "呵呵。那么今天也特别认真地给你做吧。",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "谢谢...",
      "fullImage": "end_true",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_021"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "ecstatic_openmouth",
      "text": "快点...拜托了...♡",
      "fullImage": "end_true",
      "voiceFile": "ending_true_022"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "(完美...她已经完全是我的了...!)",
      "fullImage": "end_true"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈的身体已经敏感到无法正常生活的程度。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "爬楼梯就会高潮，无法忍受电车的震动，上课时也要按着胯部忍耐。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "乳头始终勃起，私处24小时湿润，没有{{playerName}}的治疗就无法保持正常状态。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "奈奈为了寻求快感每天都来整体院。\n这已经成为了我和她的日常。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "【TRUE END】",
      "triggerEnding": "true"
    }
  ]
}
